        <title>Node.js 工廠模式 (Factory Design Pattern)</title>
        <link>https://blog.marplek.online/p/node.js-%E5%B7%A5%E5%BB%A0%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F-factory-design-pattern/</link>
